channel.title: Auto Email Account Creator
channel.description:
Yes, i would like if someone would want to make some kind of email account creating program. I dont care if it is for Hotmail, Lycos or Yahoo, it just has to be free. Why i want it? Because if i can make accounts easily, i can make a lot and then use them for free RapidShare accounts which i will post here. If someone make a program like this, i think it is the easyest in java, i will give you rep++, or maybe rep+++ or much rep :P.
Pim Jong
